915
01:01:45,285 --> 01:01:46,328
Aku mulai khawatir.

916
01:01:55,086 --> 01:01:56,171
Apakah ada yang salah?

917
01:01:59,591 --> 01:02:01,134
Halo?

918
01:02:10,310 --> 01:02:12,770
Halo?

919
01:02:12,771 --> 01:02:14,146
Siapa ini?

920
01:02:14,147 --> 01:02:15,898
Hei.

921
01:02:15,899 --> 01:02:17,232
